    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i get the \"double edged sword\" thing, but it feels like you're leaning a bit more on the \"dangerous\" side. like, isn't it kind of a stretch to say it leads to authoritarianism just because people care about their country? can't you have a healthy sense of national pride without it becoming a problem?",
